This project aim to recreate an IRC (Internet Relay Chat) program.

SERVER:
	- create a Server, and save INFOS (owner, date of creation, ...)
	- listen for incoming connection, every new connection is a user
	- link each new connection to a User structure
	- parse every input to check if its a command

CLIENT:
	- prompt user for its login, display a list of Servers to connect to, and
		prompt for wich to connect.
	- once connected, get a list of the available channels

COMMANDS:
	INFO <target>: describe the server, uptime, number of connected people,...
